Audio data (wav files) and hiragana-only text data (transcribe-hiragana.txt) may be used only in the following cases:
- Research at academic institutions
- Research for non-commercial purposes, including research at for-profit organizations
- Personal use for non-commercial purposes

The mixed kanji-kana text data (transcribe-text.txt) is licensed under CC BY in accordance with the copyright of the "Advanced Medical Conference".

